OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBrightest first thing, with the
OL,6,Fbest sunny spells in the east. Cloud
OL,7,Fgenerally increasing from the west
OL,8,Fthrough morning. Cloudier during the
OL,9,Fafternoon, with the wind picking up,
OL,10,Fbut feeling warm after a chilly start
OL,11,Fin places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBecoming windy during the
OL,14,Fevening, with blustery sharp showers
OL,15,Fmaking inroads eastwards towards
OL,16,Fmidnight. Drier, with clearer spells
OL,17,Fspreading from the west towards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
