OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cooler-feeling day, with a
OL,6,Ffew showers in northern parts dying
OL,7,Faway to leave an increasingly fine day
OL,8,Fgenerally, with some sunshine breaking
OL,9,Fthrough. Winds easing, becoming light
OL,10,Fby evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,13,Ffine through this period, with some
OL,14,Fwarm days and sunny periods after
OL,15,Fchilly starts, with a slight frost
OL,16,Fperhaps starting Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
